title: Hvordan dabbe
content:
The basics of the dab

Just hit the nasty dab bro forreal. It is easy as heck.

The breakdown

Ok you hit it like fatty, then you whip it hard as heck man. It is quite exquisite and easy when you get the hang of it. It is all in the swing of the elbow and the angle you whip it on. You don't want to whip it at the wrong angle.This image above describes the perfect angle of the arms during the execution of the dab.
